    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;abjuration;\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Cleric 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a small parchment with a bit of holy text written upon it)<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Target:</strong>&nbsp;creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;1 Minute/Level<br>\n    <strong>Power Points/Spell Points Cost:</strong>&nbsp;1<br>\n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless)\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\nThis spell creates a shimmering, magical field around the touched creature that averts attacks. The spell grants the subject a +2 deflection bonus to AC, with an additional +1 to the bonus for every six levels you have (maximum +5 deflection bonus at 18th level).\n</p><p><i>Material Component: </i>A small parchment with a bit of holy text written upon it.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
